Create com.loanflow.identity.dto.auth.LoginRequestDto in identity-service:

@Getter
@NoArgsConstructor
@AllArgsConstructor
@Builder
public class LoginRequestDto {

    @NotBlank(message = "Username is required")
    private String username;

    @NotBlank(message = "Password is required")
    private String password;
}

spring-boot-starter-validation is already pulled in transitively by spring-boot-starter-web — no additional dependency needed.

